---
title: Hearty Vegetable Stew with cheesy crostini
description: Rich, hearty, warming. These are some of the words that probably spring to mind when you think about a classic comfort dish. They're also exactly the adjectives we'd use to describe this delicious vegetable stew and its accompanying cheesy crostini.
